练习2.4
#include<iostream>
#include "Sales_item.h"

int main(){
   unsigned u = 10, u2 = 42;
   std::cout << u2 - u << std::endl;
   std::cout << u - u2 << std::endl;

   int i = 10, i2 = 42;
   std::cout << i2 - i << std::endl;
   std::cout << i - i2 << std::endl;
   std::cout << i - u << std::endl;
   std::cout << u - i << std::endl;
}

---------------------2.1.3节练习------------------------
练习2.5
1) 'a':char  L'a':宽字符  "a":string  L"a":宽字符串
2)  10:int   10u:unsigned int  10L:long  10uL:unsigned long  012:八进制  0xc:十六进制
3)  3.14:float  3.14f:float  3.14L:long double
4)  10:int  10u:unsigned int  10.:     10e-2:float

练习2.6
有区别，第一行是二进制，第二行是八进制

